#

Spicy Chipotle Guacamole

10 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerSnackVegan

Description

A creamy and spicy twist on classic guacamole, perfect for dipping or as a topping!

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic, minced: 1 clove
  • cherry tomatoes, chopped: 1/2 cup
  • red onion, finely chopped: 1/4 cup
  • fresh cilantro, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • chipotle peppers in adobo sauce, minced: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
